      "content": "For a high-status look, aim for understated luxury—think perfectly tailored, classic silhouettes in neutral tones, avoiding anything too flashy or overtly trendy. When it comes to speech, adopt a measured, formal tone, speaking slowly and deliberately to convey authority rather than rushing to fill silence. The key is projecting an aura of effortless control, which is often best achieved by mirroring the most reserved and polished individuals in the room.",
